Filecoin Testnet miningFilecoin 测试网挖矿

Updated as of December 13th, 2019更新于 2019 年 12 月 13 日

Becoming a Filecoin miner is an opportunity for community members to help store and preserve access to humanity’s most important information. By providing network security and infrastructure, Filecoin miners help build a more open, resilient, and trustworthy Internet.成为 Filecoin 矿工是社区成员帮助存储和保留对人类最重要信息的访问的机会。通过提供网络安全和基础设施，Filecoin 矿工帮助建立一个更开放、更有弹性和更值得信赖的互联网。

Filecoin mining is a novel opportunity to earn revenue from providing data storage and retrieval services to clients across a vast network. Miners earn fees by storing and retrieving client information on the Filecoin network. The more client data a Filecoin miner stores, the more that miner’s storage power grows. More storage power on the network means it is more likely a specific miner can generate blocks and win block rewards. Miners can choose whether to participate in storage power consensus, storage mining, and/or retrieval mining. We anticipate many miners will provide focused, specialized services within these categories.Filecoin 挖矿是一个新的机会，可以通过为庞大网络中的客户提供数据存储和检索服务来赚取收入。矿工通过在 Filecoin 网络上存储和检索客户信息来赚取费用。 Filecoin 矿工存储的客户端数据越多，矿工的存储能力就增长得越多。网络上更多的存储能力意味着特定矿工更有可能生成区块并赢得区块奖励。矿工可以选择是否参与存储算力共识、存储挖矿和/或检索挖矿。我们预计许多矿工将在这些类别中提供有针对性的专业服务。

The mining hardware you put on the Filecoin network will provide useful data storage services for clients in addition to providing network security and block production. This differentiates mining on the Filecoin network from traditional Proof-of-Work networks.您放置在 Filecoin 网络上的挖矿硬件除了提供网络安全和区块生产之外，还将为客户提供有用的数据存储服务。这将 Filecoin 网络上的挖掘与传统的工作量证明网络区分开来。

Reallocating excess storage capacity to run Filecoin nodes turns your once latent storage assets into a secure storage service. The block production, storage and retrieval services that miners provide are incredibly valuable to Filecoin’s ecosystem. By bringing many miners and storage providers together in a decentralized network, Filecoin unites storage providers in the first-ever algorithmic marketplace for hiring data storage.重新分配多余的存储容量以运行 Filecoin 节点，将您曾经的潜在存储资产转变为安全的存储服务。矿工提供的块生产、存储和检索服务对 Filecoin 的生态系统具有难以置信的价值。通过将许多矿工和存储提供商聚集在一个去中心化网络中，Filecoin 将存储提供商联合到有史以来第一个租用数据存储的算法市场中。

Ready to hear more? Keep reading to understand how to get started.准备好听更多了吗？继续阅读以了解如何开始。

How to Join the Filecoin Testnet如何加入 Filecoin 测试网

To join the upcoming Filecoin testnet, you’ll need appropriate hardware and to install and set up the lotus implementation. For more information about installation and setup, please see the lotus docs.要加入即将推出的 Filecoin 测试网，您需要合适的硬件并安装和设置 Lotus 实施。有关安装和设置的更多信息，请参阅 lotus 文档。

Next, you’ll need to pledge filecoin tokens as collateral to set up your miner. “Pledge collateral” is an initial amount of filecoin that is required to join the network as a storage miner. A miner must also deposit more “deal collateral” over time as it enters each additional storage deal with clients. Collateral is deployed on the network to ensure miners behave appropriately, and it is denominated in FIL tokens. Details about collateral will be finalized in the Filecoin spec over the coming weeks. During testnet, you can retrieve test filecoin from our network faucet to use as collateral to start mining. Test filecoin do not have any value – the official filecoin tokens will not be released until mainnet launch.接下来，您需要质押 filecoin 代币作为抵押品来设置您的矿工。 “质押抵押品”是作为存储矿工加入网络所需的初始 filecoin 数量。随着时间的推移，矿工还必须在与客户进行每笔额外的存储交易时存入更多的“交易抵押品”。抵押品部署在网络上以确保矿工的行为适当，并以 FIL 代币计价。有关抵押品的详细信息将在未来几周内在 Filecoin 规范中最终确定。在测试网期间，您可以从我们的网络水龙头中检索测试文件币，用作开始挖矿的抵押品。测试 filecoin 没有任何价值——官方 filecoin 令牌将在主网启动之前不会发布。

Protocol Labs’ Standard Hardware Testing ConfigurationProtocol Labs 的标准硬件测试配置

(please read carefully)（请仔细阅读）

CAUTION: This section describes the standard testing configuration the Protocol Labs team has used to test Filecoin storage mining on the lotus implementation. There is no guarantee this testing configuration will be suitable for Filecoin storage mining at mainnet launch. If you need to buy new hardware to join the Filecoin testnet, we recommend to buy no more hardware than you require for testing.注意：本节描述了协议实验室团队用于测试 Lotus 实现上的 Filecoin 存储挖掘的标准测试配置。无法保证此测试配置适用于主网启动时的 Filecoin 存储挖掘。如果您需要购买新硬件来加入 Filecoin 测试网，我们建议您购买的硬件不要超过测试所需的数量。

Our standard testing configuration is one of many possibilities for Filecoin testnet mining. We expect testnet miners to find additional hardware combinations, some of which might be more efficient than the testing configuration described below. If you’re running lotus with alternate hardware configurations, please run the lotus benchmarking tool and post your results in this thread.我们的标准测试配置是 Filecoin 测试网挖掘的众多可能性之一。我们希望测试网矿工找到额外的硬件组合，其中一些可能比下面描述的测试配置更有效。如果您使用其他硬件配置运行 Lotus，请运行 Lotus 基准测试工具并将您的结果发布到此线程中。

Sector sizes and minimum pledged storage required to mine blocks are two very important Filecoin testnet parameters that impact hardware decisions. We will continue to refine these parameters (and other proofs parameters) during testnet. Because of this, our standard testing configuration for Filecoin mainnet may change.扇区大小和挖掘块所需的最小质押存储是影响硬件决策的两个非常重要的 Filecoin 测试网参数。我们将在测试网期间继续完善这些参数（和其他证明参数）。因此，我们的 Filecoin 主网标准测试配置可能会发生变化。

Sector Sizes: If you choose to purchase hardware to test on the Filecoin testnet, we recommend you buy computational hardware that will support sealing 32GiB sectors. Testnet will temporarily support 1GiB “test-sectors” so miners can easily on-board to the network. This small sector size is not realistic for mainnet. We will perform a fork upgrade to discontinue support for 1GiB “test-sectors” after testnet launch, and will announce the timing and mechanics of the upgrade on our blog.扇区大小：如果您选择购买硬件在 Filecoin 测试网上进行测试，我们建议您购买支持密封 32GiB 扇区的计算硬件。 Testnet 将暂时支持 1GiB“测试扇区”，以便矿工可以轻松加入网络。这种小扇区大小对于主网来说是不现实的。我们将在测试网启动后执行分叉升级以停止对 1GiB“测试扇区”的支持，并将在我们的博客上公布升级的时间和机制。

Miner Size: To be eligible for block mining during testnet (not just accepting storage deals), a miner must pledge at least 512GiB of disk storage. This requirement will likely increase for Filecoin mainnet. If you’re only interested in participating in storage deals, you can join the network with less storage. However, your proven storage will not count towards total network power and will not enable you to earn block rewards if you currently have under 512GiB pledged to the network.矿工大小：为了有资格在测试网期间进行区块挖掘（不仅仅是接受存储交易），矿工必须承诺至少 512GiB 的磁盘存储。对于 Filecoin 主网，此要求可能会增加。如果您只对参与存储交易感兴趣，您可以加入存储较少的网络。但是，如果您目前向网络承诺的存储容量不足 512GiB，您已证明的存储将不计入总网络功率，并且不会使您获得区块奖励。

Below is the configuration we have tested for sealing 32GiB sectors on lotus. The configuration is based on the steps required in the Filecoin mining process. We made specific trade-offs related to computational power in our standard testing configuration (i.e., we allocate resources for GPUs instead of more CPU power). It is possible to mine on testnet with other configurations, but since we haven’t tested all of them, we will not cover their viability or performance in this post.下面是我们测试过的用于在 Lotus 上密封 32GiB 扇区的配置。配置基于 Filecoin 挖掘过程中所需的步骤。我们在标准测试配置中做出了与计算能力相关的特定权衡（即，我们为 GPU 分配资源而不是更多的 CPU 能力）。可以使用其他配置在测试网上挖矿，但由于我们尚未测试所有配置，因此我们不会在本文中介绍它们的可行性或性能。

Storage贮存

Filecoin rewards miners for the storage they provide to the network. Miners should be able to use most commodity HDDs, SSDs, or other types of disks to provide bulk storage to the network, and it is to the miner’s advantage to architect a system that allows for scaling addition of harddrives.Filecoin 奖励矿工为网络提供的存储。矿工应该能够使用大多数商品 HDD、SSD 或其他类型的磁盘为网络提供大容量存储，并且构建一个允许扩展硬盘驱动器的系统对矿工有利。

Filecoin is relatively unopinionated about the form of storage provided to the network, however it is important to reiterate that the storage medium used for providing storage to the network will be read during Election PoSt. For this reason, we recommend choosing a storage medium that can perform reads quickly (i.e., not cold storage).Filecoin 对提供给网络的存储形式相对没有意见，但重要的是要重申，用于向网络提供存储的存储介质将在 Election PoSt 期间被读取。因此，我们建议选择可以快速执行读取的存储介质（即非冷存储）。

Currently in our testing configuration, a commodity harddrive provided sufficient read speeds to fit within the ElectionPoSt epoch window. Miners should consider the time budget allotted for Election PoSt and derive their own requirements based on the speed of their network and compute resources. For more information about Election PoSt, please see Proof-of-Spacetime.目前在我们的测试配置中，商品硬盘驱动器提供了足够的读取速度以适应 ElectionPoSt 时代窗口。矿工应该考虑分配给 Election PoSt 的时间预算，并根据他们的网络速度和计算资源得出他们自己的要求。有关 Election PoSt 的更多信息，请参阅时空证明。

Proof-of-Replication复制证明

We’re testing with a powerful CPU (with at least 8 cores) to replicate client data during Proof-of-Replication (“PoRep”). A powerful CPU allows a miner to process data faster and generate PoReps more quickly to gain power on the network.我们正在使用功能强大的 CPU（至少 8 个内核）进行测试，以在复制证明（“PoRep”）期间复制客户端数据。强大的 CPU 允许矿工更快地处理数据并更快地生成 PoReps，从而在网络上获得权力。

The replication process utilizes fast disks for offloading data from memory onto disk. For this we’ve tested with SSDs (512GB) that function as a large cache to store unsealed sectors-in-transit (during the pre-commit and commit phases of PoRep) and to cache during the sealing process.复制过程利用快速磁盘将数据从内存卸载到磁盘上。为此，我们使用 SSD (512GB) 进行了测试，该 SSD 用作大型缓存以存储未密封的传输中扇区（在 PoRep 的预提交和提交阶段）并在密封过程中进行缓存。

Our standard configuration also runs with a large amount of RAM (128GB). RAM is needed to compute data replication in memory, and currently has a 2-3x relationship to sector size. The circuits we designed to run during SNARK generation in both PoRep and PoSt are very large and will consume a significant amount of RAM. These large circuits minimize the footprint of the SNARK output of proofs for efficient on-chain submission.我们的标准配置还使用大量 RAM (128GB) 运行。需要 RAM 来计算内存中的数据复制，目前与扇区大小有 2-3 倍的关系。我们设计用于在 PoRep 和 PoSt 中生成 SNARK 期间运行的电路非常大，并且会消耗大量 RAM。这些大型电路最大限度地减少了 SNARK 证明输出的足迹，以实现高效的链上提交。

We also use significant GPU power to generate SNARKs in a more time-efficient and cost-effective way. SNARKs are generated on PoRep proofs of each sealed replica and the SNARK output is submitted to the chain. We specifically note the lotus implementation is designed for NVIDIA-manufactured GPU chips, however, we anticipate supporting cards from other manufacturers in the future. As we continue to fine-tune our proofs parameters, we expect mainnet circuits to require more computational power than testnet circuits.我们还使用强大的 GPU 能力以更省时且更具成本效益的方式生成 SNARK。在每个密封副本的 PoRep 证明上生成 SNARK，并将 SNARK 输出提交给链。我们特别注意到 lotus 实现是为 NVIDIA 制造的 GPU 芯片设计的，但是，我们预计将来会支持来自其他制造商的卡。随着我们继续微调我们的证明参数，我们预计主网电路需要比测试网电路更多的计算能力。

We observed in our testing that it can be more efficient to have multiple “sealing machines” working across a range of storage instead of running the entire set of Filecoin mining processes on a single machine (sealing and PoSt). This allows a miner to efficiently run multiple processes at a time.我们在测试中观察到，让多个“封存机”在一定范围的存储上工作比在一台机器上运行整套 Filecoin 挖掘过程（封存和 PoSt）效率更高。这允许矿工一次高效地运行多个进程。

Proof-of-Spacetime时空证明

Our test configuration accounts for storage overhead – we currently estimate overhead as 2x pledged storage, but this could change for mainnet. We’re currently running ~1.5TB in disk storage for sealed sectors, but we believe there are more efficient ways to configure sealed storage to reduce overhead. We’re also testing with fast and parallelized disk access to sealed sectors for generating tickets to potentially win election tickets for block rewards in Election Proof-of-Spacetime(“ElectionPoSt”).我们的测试配置考虑了存储开销——我们目前估计开销为 2 倍的质押存储，但这可能会因主网而改变。我们目前为密封扇区运行约 1.5TB 的磁盘存储，但我们相信有更有效的方法来配置密封存储以减少开销。 We’re also testing with fast and parallelized disk access to sealed sectors for generating tickets to potentially win election tickets for block rewards in Election Proof-of-Spacetime(“ElectionPoSt”).

When running PoSt processes, our current testing configuration stores sealed sectors on hard disks that continually operate (24⁄7) due to frequent reads for submitting PoSt.在运行 PoSt 进程时，我们当前的测试配置将密封扇区存储在硬盘上，这些扇区由于频繁读取以提交 PoSt 而连续运行 (24⁄7)。

SNARKs are run during ElectionPoSt only if a miner has winning election tickets for earning block rewards during a given epoch period. Our configuration uses GPU power to compute PoSt SNARKs output well within (~20 seconds) each epoch period each time our miner wins an election ticket. GPU power needed for PoSt largely depends on how many winning election tickets a miner has during any given epoch, which is related to their proportion of storage in the network.仅在矿工在给定时期获得盖帽奖励的选举门票时，SNARKS才能在选举店期间运行。 Our configuration uses GPU power to compute PoSt SNARKs output well within (~20 seconds) each epoch period each time our miner wins an election ticket. PoSt 所需的 GPU 能力在很大程度上取决于矿工在任何给定时期内拥有多少张获胜的选举票，这与他们在网络中的存储比例有关。

We also suggest a relatively low latency network connection to submit PoSt on time. If a miner fails to submit PoSt on time many times, it could lead to winning fewer block rewards and increase the risk of being slashed.我们还建议使用延迟相对较低的网络连接来按时提交 PoSt。如果矿工多次未能按时提交 PoSt，可能会导致获得更少的区块奖励并增加被罚没的风险。

For more information about how the ElectionPoSt process relates to mining hardware, see our diagram below:有关 ElectionPoSt 过程如何与挖矿硬件相关的更多信息，请参见下图：

Filecoin Mining is NOT Proof-of-Work GPU MiningFilecoin 挖矿不是工作证明 GPU 挖矿

Remember, Filecoin mining is based on storage power consensus: having more power on the network (proven storage) is directly related to winning more block rewards. The amount of a miner’s power on the network is linear with respect to the amount of storage the miner puts on the network, not the amount of GPUs it runs. By comparison, in Proof-of-Work GPU mining, a miner must compete on GPU power to win block rewards. In Filecoin mining, a miner competes on storage power consensus and not GPU power. Miners use GPUs during ElectionPoSt only if they have winning election tickets. The best and cheapest way to gain power is by adding more useful storage to the Filecoin network.请记住，Filecoin 挖矿基于存储能力共识：在网络上拥有更多权力（经过验证的存储）与赢得更多区块奖励直接相关。矿工在网络上的算力与矿工在网络上放置的存储量成线性关系，而不是它运行的 GPU 数量。相比之下，在工作量证明 GPU 挖矿中，矿工必须在 GPU 算力上竞争才能赢得区块奖励。在 Filecoin 挖矿中，矿工竞争的是存储能力共识，而不是 GPU 能力。矿工只有在获得选举票时才会在 ElectionPoSt 期间使用 GPU。获得权力的最好和最便宜的方法是向 Filecoin 网络添加更多有用的存储。

If you’re a smaller miner worried about the cost of GPUs, rest assured that we’re working to enable miners to securely outsource SNARK computation to third party service providers.如果您是担心 GPU 成本的小型矿工，请放心，我们正在努力使矿工能够安全地将 SNARK 计算外包给第三方服务提供商。

Now that you know about the gear, get ready to put it to work! You’ll have the opportunity to join the lotus testnet soon.现在您已经了解了齿轮，准备好投入使用吧！您很快就会有机会加入 Lotus 测试网。
